title: PFI Empathy (Neighbour)
subtitle: When my neighborhood succeeds, I feel good
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)

title: PFI Shared Fate (Neighbour)
subtitle: My neighborhood and I rise and fall together
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)

title: PFI Empathy (Humanity)
subtitle: When all of humanity succeeds, I feel good
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)

title: PFI Shared Fate (Humanity)
subtitle: All of humanity and I rise and fall together
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)

title: Willingness to help (Neighbor)
subtitle: Someone from your neighborhood is having their\nhouse fixed, so it isn't livable. How willing would you\nbe to let them move into your house for a week?
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = not at all willing, 7 = very willing)

title: Willingness to help (Humanity)
subtitle: A displaced person who is not a citizen of your own country\nis having their house fixed, so it isn't livable. How willing would\nyou be to let them move into your house for a week?
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = not at all willing, 7 = very willing)

title: NBT (Neighbor)
subtitle: Helping someone from my neighborhood when\nthey are in need is the right thing to do
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = strongly disagree, 7 = strongly agree)

title: NBT (Humanity)
subtitle: Helping a person who is not a citizen of your own\ncountry when they are in need is the right thing to do
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = strongly disagree, 7 = strongly agree)

title: Perception of COVID-19 risk
subtitle: How likely do you think it is that you will contract /\nbecome infected with COVID19?
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = not at all, 7 = extremely)

title: Risk Management (Reduction)
subtitle: I try to reduce my risk of getting COVID19 by\ndoing things like washing my hands often
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)

title: Risk Management (Retention)
subtitle: I have been stocking up on food and supplies\nso that I am prepared for the COVID19 epidemic
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)

title: Risk Management (Transfer)
subtitle: I am likely to ask parents or friends for help\npreparing for the COVID19 epidemic
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)

title: Risk Management (Avoidance)
subtitle: I completely avoid situations that could put\nme at risk of contracting COVID19
ylab: Mean +/- SE\n(1 = do not agree at all, 7 = strongly agree)
